txt.en: Orcs patrol the woods in great numbers, likely pouring down from Isengard through the Balewood to the north-west.
You have defeated a number of the Orc-invaders pouring in from Isengard through the Balewood, making the Whitshaws safer for a short time, at least.
Orcs can be found in the woods of the northern Whitshaws.\n\nYou should defeat the Orcs pouring in from Isengard through the Balewood.
